{"root":{"data":{"text":"四大天王：\n氢、氧、碳、氮","font-size":32,"color":"white"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcay9hc00","created":1531725409572,"text":"氢（H）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-203.7499969638884,"y":-74.99999888241302},"font-size":32,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcef0de04","created":1531725417115,"text":"简介：宇宙中含量高，但在地球大气中含量低，其原因是因为氢太轻了。氢是宇宙的燃料。","background":"#eaf1dd","font-size":24,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcep7pts0","created":1531725417732,"text":"用途：火箭使用液氢与液氧作为燃料发生反应，形成温度极高的蒸汽从喷管喷出，由此产生的爆炸气浪，推动火箭上升","background":"#eaf1dd","font-size":24,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcf2d0944","created":1531725418527,"text":"实验现象：氢气燃烧，发出蓝色火焰，放出热量","background":"#eaf1dd","font-size":24,"layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcbcwynks","created":1531725410458,"text":"氧（O）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-207.49999690800905,"y":-31.24999953433877},"font-size":32,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcg6re8wg","created":1531725420970,"text":"简介：由于出现了生命，导致地球大气中氧气含量增多。氧是地球的助燃剂。","background":"#eaf1dd","font-size":24,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcgkocy88","created":1531725421811,"text":"性质：无色无味的气体，密度比空气略大，不可燃，能助燃，能供给呼吸，不易溶于水;氧气在氧化反应中提供了氧，其具有氧化性","background":"#eaf1dd","font-size":24,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzchpiq6g4","created":1531725424281,"text":"实验现象：带有火星的木条在氧气中能够复燃，说明氧气能支持燃烧","background":"#eaf1dd","font-size":24,"layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcbq52q88","created":1531725411258,"text":"碳（C）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-211.2499968521297,"y":33.749999497085696},"font-size":32,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcig81sg8","created":1531725425896,"text":"简介：人类最早发现并利用的元素之一。化石燃料（煤、石油、天然气）是我们最熟悉的碳的存在形式","font-size":24,"background":"#eaf1dd","layout_right_offset":{"x":4,"y":16},"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzciu1raos","created":1531725426732,"text":"用途：碳可以形成软软的石墨，用于铅笔芯和焊条，石墨可以导电；碳还可以形成最硬的天然物质——金刚石，用于切割和钻戒。","font-size":24,"background":"#eaf1dd","layout_right_offset":{"x":-1.499999888241291,"y":18.000000000000114},"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcj59ws0s","created":1531725427410,"text":"特点：碳是活体细胞结构的组成成分，碳构成了蛋白质、脂肪、碳水化合物以及DNA双螺旋结构的骨架。\n没有碳，就没有生命。碳是形成有机物的重要条件。","font-size":24,"background":"#eaf1dd","layout_right_offset":{"x":2,"y":14},"layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcc26hswk","created":1531725411986,"text":"氮（N）","layout_right_offset":{"x":-214.99999679625034,"y":56.24999916180968},"layout":null,"font-size":32},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmxzcjwd49sk","created":1531725429048,"text":"简介：氮气是空气的主要成分，不活泼，也不支持燃烧。","background":"#eaf1dd","layout":null,"font-size":24},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d3o4kzey9i80","created":1724500993044,"text":"用途：德国科学家哈伯，发明了人工合成氨的技术，被称为人类历史上最为重要的发明之一。\n氮是农作物必需的物质之一，但只有极少数农作物可以直接吸收利用空气中的氮。","font-size":24,"background":"#eaf1dd","layout_right_offset":{"x":-3.7499956972897053,"y":13.749999795109034},"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmxzcks06s8c","created":1531725430962,"text":"特点：氮是氨基酸的组成元素，而氨基酸是构成蛋白质的基本单元，\n蛋白质是构成细胞的重要物质。","background":"#eaf1dd","layout_right_offset":{"x":0,"y":19.999999701976776},"layout":null,"font-size":24},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}